    "quantization-bay": {
      "description": "The Quantization Bay where heavy models are compressed into lean, deployable forms. INT8 calipers measure every weight, and knowledge distillation funnels pour wisdom from large teachers into small students. The fleet's edge deployments depend on what happens here.",
