    "prompt-laboratory": {
      "description": "The Prompt Laboratory where the art and science of instruction engineering converge. Chains of thought crystallize, few-shot examples are catalogued, and system prompts undergo rigorous testing. Every word matters here \u2014 the right prompt unlocks capabilities hidden in the weights.",
      "exits": {
